  "decision_conditions": [
    "By reason of the inadequate size and quality of the internal living accommodation and external amenity areas, the development would fail to provide acceptable standards of amenity for future occupiers contrary to Policies DMH 1, DMHB 16, DMHB 18 of the The Hillingdon Local Plan: Part 2 - Development Management Policies (2020); Policy D6 of the London Plan 2021 and the NPPF in particular Paragraph 123.",
    "The proposals would result in the loss of a three bedroom family sized home which would not be re-provided and the development would consequently have a detrimental impact on the supply of larger family sized homes, for which there is an identified need within the borough, therefore the proposals fail to provide an appropriate housing mix contrary to Policies DMH 1 and DMH 2 of the The Hillingdon Local Plan: Part 2 - Development Management Policies (2020); Policies H2 and H10 of the London Plan 2021; and the NPPF in particular Paragraph 60."
